a.com/symbol/XME\" title=\"SPDR\u00ae S&amp;P Metals and Mining ETF\">XME</a></span>) is an exchange-traded fund that invests in U.S. metals and mining companies. The fund seeks to replicate the performance of its chosen benchmark, which is the S&amp;P Metals &amp; Mining Select Industry Index from </p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1796832170/image_1796832170.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742861-xme-metals-and-mining-stocks-are-cyclically-well-positioned-but-not-cheap", "pub_date": "2024-12-08 12:20:15"}, {"id": "4742857", "title": "DAPP: Digital Assets Are Here To Stay, Just Hold Tight Right Now", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1347310666/image_1347310666.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"processor chip, tech environment, blockchain concept\" data-id=\"1347310666\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"864px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1347310666/image_1347310666.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1347310666/image_1347310666.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1347310666/image_1347310666.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1347310666/image_1347310666.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1347310666/image_1347310666.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1347310666/image_1347310666.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1347310666/image_1347310666.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1347310666/image_1347310666.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">blackdovfx</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Digital transformation across businesses and individuals has been a trend for years, as our technology-driven world continues to shift. This digitalization feels less like a trend, and more like an imperative asset to our daily functioning at home and in the workplace. The</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1347310666/image_1347310666.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742857-dapp-digital-assets-are-here-to-stay-just-hold-tight-right-now", "pub_date": "2024-12-08 11:53:49"}, {"id": "4742855", "title": "Mexico Fund: Attractively Valued With A Stable Outlook In MXN Terms", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1221531535/image_1221531535.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Mexican Flag Major Shopping Street Zocalo Puebla Mexico\" data-id=\"1221531535\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1047px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1221531535/image_1221531535.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1221531535/image_1221531535.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1221531535/image_1221531535.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1221531535/image_1221531535.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1221531535/image_1221531535.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1221531535/image_1221531535.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1221531535/ima