ages/1303850380/image_1303850380.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1303850380/image_1303850380.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1303850380/image_1303850380.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1303850380/image_1303850380.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1303850380/image_1303850380.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1303850380/image_1303850380.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1303850380/image_1303850380.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">marchmeena29</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>EQIN strategy</h2> <p>Columbia U.S. Equity Income ETF (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSEARCA:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/EQIN\" title=\"Columbia U.S. Equity Income ETF\">EQIN</a></span>) is an actively managed ETF launched on 6/13/2016. It has a portfolio of 100 stocks, a 30-day SEC yield of 2.24%, and an expense ratio of 0.35%.</p> <p>As described in</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1303850380/image_1303850380.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742840-eqin-good-value-etf-but-value-still-out-of-style", "pub_date": "2024-12-08 09:55:27"}]}